OriginalText.Phrase: quos Jnter ramus supereminet altior vnus

Note.EditorialCommentary: F in LonBLR 11 E.xi. That reading could be accepted as a deliberate contrapuntal imperfection, directly comparable to the unprepared fourth in mm. 38-9 of Josquin's En lombre dung buyssonet, the rustic model of the present composition (see Introduction/Notes).
